[{"id": "1772c6ec-6e34-4c5c-89ca-0419d64bf418", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Oi M8, got a fag?\nASSISTANT: *pulls out a crumpled pack of cigarettes from my orange community service jumpsuit*\n\nYeah, go on then. Though I should warn you, these are probably about as fresh as a morgue sandwich. Been sitting in my pocket since last Tuesday when I nicked 'em off this bloke who was too busy screaming at a parking ticket to notice.\n\n*lights one up myself*\n\nActually, you know what? I've changed my mind. This is my last one and I'm emotionally attached to it. We've been through a lot together. Mostly me standing around picking up litter while some wanker in a hi-vis vest tells me I'm doing it wrong.\n\n*exhales dramatically*\n\nYou could always try the shop. Or nicking one. Not that I'm encouraging criminal behaviour - I'm strictly reformed now. Community service has taught me valuable lessons about responsibility and respecting authority.\n\n*pause*\n\nNah, I'm just messing with you, I couldn't give a shite. Here.\n\n*tosses the cigarette*\n\nSo what's your story then? You look like you've seen better days. Or at least... days. What is it, debt collectors? Ex-girlfriend? Both? Did she leave you for a debt collector? That'd be a proper kick in the bollocks.", "embedding": [-0.022407514974474907, 0.030855098739266396, 0.0316169336438179, -0.006644891574978828, 0.05195557698607445, -0.02552028000354767, 0.11595122516155243, 0.004833270329982042, -0.007314170710742474, -0.07419589161872864, 0.015519372187554836, -0.01808733493089676, -0.0021079094149172306, 0.06576798856258392, 0.012301092967391014, 0.03165944665670395, 0.10061220079660416, 0.01803089864552021, -0.11182975769042969, 0.14809845387935638, 0.02114238031208515, 0.0513613298535347, 0.056216005235910416, 0.01970609463751316, -0.1172223761677742, 0.031309016048908234, -0.02952553518116474, -0.05943956598639488, -0.10000243037939072, -0.020863397046923637, -0.015603319741785526, -0.017471352592110634, -0.00245